    <h1>As I Am</h1>
    <p> "As I Am" is a transformed version of my favourite quote in Charlotte Brontë's 'Jane Eyre': "As We Are"; where she explicitly talks about female identity and self-dependence in contrast with the society's customs.</p>

    <p>This section is always growing and shows a little bit of who I am beyond my academic work 👩🏻‍💻</p>
